Available Tools: turn_on_light | turn_off_light | set_brightness | set_color | get_light_status
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "light_id": "string", "brightness": "number", "color": "string" }
Response Schema: { "light_id": "string", "state": "string", "brightness": "number", "color": "string" }
---
Question: Turn the study reading lamp to a cool daylight shade.
Call: { "func_call": "set_color", "light_id": "read_stu_13", "brightness": null, "color": "cool daylight" }
Response: { "light_id": "read_stu_13", "state": "on", "brightness": 230, "color": "cool daylight" }

Question: Modify the library wall sconce to hex code #800080 for purple ambiance.
Call: { "func_call": "set_color", "light_id": "wall_lib_14", "brightness": null, "color": "#800080" }
Response: { "light_id": "wall_lib_14", "state": "on", "brightness": 140, "color": "#800080" }

Question: Is the laundry room overhead light currently active?
Call: { "func_call": "get_light_status", "light_id": "over_laun_15", "brightness": null, "color": null }
Response: { "light_id": "over_laun_15", "state": "off", "brightness": 0, "color": "neutral white" }

